1	BassDownload	BassDownload | Zippy Mediafire Hulk	--- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSS \nentries: \n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: Dylan Farella\n  categories: \n  - Releases\n  content: |\n    <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://bassdownload.com/2012/martin-solveig-the-night-out-a-trak-remix/a-trak/" rel="attachment wp-att-6330"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-6330" title="a-trak" src="http://bassdownload.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/a-trak.jpg" alt="" width="540" height="360" /></a></p>\n    <p><strong>Martin Solveig</strong> is prepping is upcoming <strong>&#8220;The Night Out&#8221;</strong> EP and has called upon <strong>A-Trak</strong> to remix the title track. The Night Out has become popular as a mainstream song with minimal house music sound attached. EDM fans hold their breathe no longer as A-Trak has put that electro spin on the track for us.</p>\n    <iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" src="http://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F36950673&amp;auto_play=false&amp;show_artwork=true&amp;color=ff000d"></iframe>\n\n  entry_id: http://bassdownload.com/?p=6328\n  published: 2012-02-19 17:04:32 Z\n  summary: Martin Solveig is prepping is upcoming &#8220;The Night Out&#8221; EP and has called upon A-Trak to remix the title track. The Night Out has become popular as a mainstream song with minimal house music sound attached. EDM fans hold their &#8230; <a href="http://bassdownload.com/2012/martin-solveig-the-night-out-a-trak-remix/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>\n  title: "Martin Solveig \\xE2\\x80\\x93 The Night Out (A-Trak Remix)"\n  url: http://bassdownload.com/2012/martin-solveig-the-night-out-a-trak-remix/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: Dylan Farella\n  categories: \n  - Preview\n  content: |\n    <p><a href="http://bassdownload.com/2012/miike-snow-devils-work-dirty-south-remix-preview/dirty-south1/" rel="attachment wp-att-6324"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6324" title="Dirty-South1" src="http://bassdownload.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Dirty-South1.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="336" /></a></p>\n    <p><strong>Dirty South</strong> has the ability to turn ordinary tracks into mainline remixes including &#8216;Grand Canyon&#8217;, &#8216;Coming Home&#8217;, and &#8216;Invisible&#8217;. Dragan has remixed <strong>Miike Snow</strong> before on a track we all know and love as &#8216;Silvia&#8217;. Friday night at Pacha NYC, Dirty South debuted his next Miike Snow remix, <strong>&#8216;Devil&#8217;s Work&#8217;</strong>.</p>\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\n    <p><iframe width="640" height="360" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/tzzdeLD73N8?fs=1&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n\n  entry_id: http://bassdownload.com/?p=6323\n  published: 2012-02-19 16:53:49 Z\n  summary: Dirty South has the ability to turn ordinary tracks into mainline remixes including &#8216;Grand Canyon&#8217;, &#8216;Coming Home&#8217;, and &#8216;Invisible&#8217;. Dragan has remixed Miike Snow before on a track we all know and love as &#8216;Silvia&#8217;. Friday night at Pacha NYC, &#8230; <a href="http://bassdownload.com/2012/miike-snow-devils-work-dirty-south-remix-preview/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>\n  title: "Miike Snow \\xE2\\x80\\x93 Devil\\xE2\\x80\\x99s Work (Dirty South Remix) [Preview]"\n  url: http://bassdownload.com/2012/miike-snow-devils-work-dirty-south-remix-preview/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: Dylan Farella\n  categories: \n  - Live Set Sundays\n  - featured\n  content: "<p style=\\"text-align: left;\\"><a href=\\"http://bassdownload.com/2012/live-set-sundays-003/swedish-house-mafia-takeover-bbc-radio-1-450x299/\\" rel=\\"attachment wp-att-6316\\"><img class=\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6316\\" title=\\"Swedish-House-Mafia-Takeover-BBC-Radio-1-450x299\\" src=\\"http://bassdownload.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Swedish-House-Mafia-Takeover-BBC-Radio-1-450x299.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"450\\" height=\\"299\\" /></a></p>\\n\\\n    <p style=\\"text-align: left;\\">It is impossible to argue that this weekend had been dominated by anyone else than Swedish House Mafia. When the trio took over Pete Tong&#8217;s 2 hour spot on BBC Radio 1, the took the world with them, debuting exclusive tracks all night long. However, we bring even more unique sets from this weekend including mixes from Tommy Trash and Hard Rock Sofa that are easy to fall in love with. Tiesto&#8217;s Club Life and Afrojack&#8217;s Jacked both made this Sunday as well.</p>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"></h3>\\n\\\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><a href=\\"http://www.mediafire.com/?6tlnys8996d43d4\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Swedish House Mafia Takeover \\xE2\\x80\\x93 BBC Radio 1 Essential Selection [Deadmau5 Guestmix]</a></h3>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"></h3>\\n\\\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><a href=\\"http://dopeshare.com/nhprdyyatkcv\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Ti\\xC3\\xABsto \\xE2\\x80\\x93 Club Life 255 [19-02-2012]</a></h3>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"></h3>\\n\\\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><a href=\\"http://dopeshare.com/m25c8zgjn28s\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Tommy Trash \\xE2\\x80\\x93 February 2012 Mix</a></h3>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"></h3>\\n\\\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><a href=\\"http://dopeshare.com/csduuncagojt\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Hard Rock Sofa \\xE2\\x80\\x93 February Mix 2012</a></h3>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"></h3>\\n\\\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><a href=\\"http://dopeshare.com/v1khj51odpxg\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Afrojack &amp; Bobby Burns \\xE2\\x80\\x93 Jacked [18-02-2012]</a></h3>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"></h3>\\n\\\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\\n\\\n    <h3 style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><a href=\\"http://ak-media.soundcloud.com/dk2IlCh0QwXB?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBHW5FB4ERKUQUOQ&amp;Expires=1329668445&amp;Signature=cWCItW7HIkXUQuwWjvmp68Piv7A%3D&amp;__gda__=1329668445_4e65825e6a5f7ae9dc7d60309003f9a1\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Imanos \\xE2\\x80\\x93 Decked Out #011 (Incl. Feenixpawl Guest Mix)</a></h3>\\n"\n  entry_id: http://bassdownload.com/?p=6313\n  published: 2012-02-19 16:30:14 Z\n  summary: It is impossible to argue that this weekend had been dominated by anyone else than Swedish House Mafia. When the trio took over Pete Tong&#8217;s 2 hour spot on BBC Radio 1, the took the world with them, debuting exclusive &#8230; <a href="http://bassdownload.com/2012/live-set-sundays-003/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>\n  title: Live Set Sundays 003\n  url: http://bassdownload.com/2012/live-set-sundays-003/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: Dylan Farella\n  categories: \n  - Preview\n  - arty trio\n  - matisse sadko trio\n  - trio axwell\n  content: |\n    <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://bassdownload.com/2012/arty-matisse-sadko-trio-preview/arty-bbc-radio-1-essential-mix-11-02-2012/" rel="attachment wp-att-6304"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-6304" title="arty-bbc-radio-1-essential-mix-11-02-2012" src="http://bassdownload.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/arty-bbc-radio-1-essential-mix-11-02-2012-700x355.jpg" alt="" width="512" height="259" /></a></p>\n    <p>Another Swedish House Mafia Madison Square Garden debut, <strong>&#8220;Trio&#8221;</strong>, was aptly named after its producers, <strong>Arty</strong> and <strong>Matisse &amp; Sadko</strong>. Matisse &amp; Sadko, who released &#8216;The Legend&#8217; on Refune, collaborated with Arty and took their studio crafted work right to Axwell. Axwell loved the track and immediately signed it to Axtone. With a preview on Pete Tong&#8217