="http://soundcloud.com/charliedarker">Charlie Darker</a></span></p>\n    <p><object height="81" width="100%"><param name="movie" value="http://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F21649082&amp;show_comments=false&amp;auto_play=false&amp;color=000000"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param> <embed allowscriptaccess="always" height="81" src="http://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F21649082&amp;show_comments=false&amp;auto_play=false&amp;color=000000" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="100%"></embed></object>   <span><a href="http://soundcloud.com/charliedarker/the-electric-dream-mord">The Electric Dream &#8211; Mord Fustang (Charlie Darker Remix)</a> by <a href="http://soundcloud.com/charliedarker">Charlie Darker</a></span></p>\n    <p>Mini-Mix<br />\n    <object height="81" width="100%"><param name="movie" value="http://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F24035523&amp;show_comments=false&amp;auto_play=false&amp;color=8d8d8d"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param> <embed allowscriptaccess="always" height="81" src="http://player.soundcloud.com/player.swf?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F24035523&amp;show_comments=false&amp;auto_play=false&amp;color=8d8d8d" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="100%"></embed></object>   <span><a href="http://soundcloud.com/charliedarker/charlie-darker-household-promo">Charlie Darker Mix for Household Management</a> by <a href="http://soundcloud.com/charliedarker">Charlie Darker</a></span></p>\n    <p>The Electric Dream (Charlie Darker Remix) &#8211; Mord Fustang<br />\n    Bassmentality (Original Mix) &#8211; Zeds Dead &#038; The Killabits<br />\n    Teething Again (Charlie Darker Remix) &#8211; Love Thy Brother<br />\n    Come Together (Beataucue Remix) &#8211; Cicada<br />\n    It&#8217;s so Hot (Torro Torro Remix) &#8211; Sheen Bros<br />\n    Ayoo (Original Mix) &#8211; Clockwork<br />\n    Love (Clockwork Remix) &#8211; Felix Cartal<br />\n    Dozer (Original Mix) &#8211; Botnek<br />\n    Astromarx (Original Mix) &#8211; Charlie Darker<br />\n    Save the World (Knife Party Remix) &#8211; Swedish House Mafia<br />\n    Angst (Original Mix) &#8211; Nero<br />\n    Blood &#038; Iron (Original Mix) &#8211; Charlie Darker<br />\n    Need Change (Original Mix) &#8211; Skrillex<br />\n    Big Shot (Original Mix) &#8211; Terrabad, Awol<br />\n    Untitled &#8211; Charlie Darker<br />\n    Bubonic (Original Mix) &#8211; Autoerotique<br />\n    Trafalgar (Original Mix) &#8211; The M Machine</p>\n    <p>Stay Filthy My Friends,<br />\n    <a href="http://thefilth.us/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/shmo-sig.png"><img src="http://thefilth.us/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/shmo-sig.png" alt="" title="shmo sig" width="100" height="54" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-3314" /></a></p>\n\n  entry_id: http://thefilth.us/?p=3828\n  published: 2011-10-10 21:15:39 Z\n  summary: It is raining in San Francisco which means it is a good day to do some music hunting across the web. I found Charlie Darker a couple weeks back and &#8230;<a class="continue_reading_link" href="http://thefilth.us/2011/10/10/charlie-is-darker-than-vader/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#187;</span></a>\n  title: Charlie is Darker than Vader\n  url: http://thefilth.us/2011/10/10/charlie-is-darker-than-vader/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: connor\n  categories: \n  - Music\n  content: |\n    <p><a href="http://thefilth.us/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/bigcrowd1.jpeg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3822" title="bigcrowd1" src="http://thefilth.us/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/bigcrowd1-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="199" /></a></p>\n    <p>It&#8217;s true! Pasquale Rotella and the rest of the stellar Insomniac team have announced that the Electric Daisy Carnival will return to the Las Vegas Motor Speedway again next summer. June 8th, 9th, and 10th have been chosen to hold the days of debauchery.</p>\n    <p><iframe width="575" height="322" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/ZdXSP2ErcTQ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n    <p>&#8220;We are thrilled to welcome the Electric Daisy Carnival back to Las Vegas and to Las Vegas Motor Speedway,&#8221; said Chris Powell, president of LVMS. &#8220;EDC in 2011 provided a tremendous boost to our local economy. Additionally, the promoter of EDC, Insomniac, demonstrated that it operates a well-organized, safe and secure event. The people at Insomniac are proven professionals, and we&#8217;re excited to work together to create an unforgettable EDC in 2012 here at LVMS.&#8221;</p>\n    <p>Electric Daisy Carnival Las Vegas was internationally recognized in September at the 2011 DJ Awards in Ibiza as the International Festival of the Year.</p>\n    <p>Pretty exciting to watch EDC evolve to what it has today. Watching the electronic scene grow from underground warehouse raves to earth shattering 230,000 person events has been quite a trip. It appears to be heading for the stars with no sign of stopping. Tickets go on sale November 1st, I recommend buying yours before the rest of the world does.</p>\n    <p>-Connoisseur</p>\n\n  entry_id: http://thefilth.us/?p=3819\n  published: 2011-10-06 23:37:23 Z\n  summary: It&#8217;s true! Pasquale Rotella and the rest of the stellar Insomniac team have announced that the Electric Daisy Carnival will return to the Las Vegas Motor Speedway again next summer. &#8230;<a class="continue_reading_link" href="http://thefilth.us/2011/10/06/edc-2012-dates-announced/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#187;</span></a>\n  title: EDC 2012 Dates Announced\n  url: http://thefilth.us/2011/10/06/edc-2012-dates-announced/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: connor\n  categories: \n  - Music\n  - camo & krooked\n  - candy land\n  - fenech-solar\n  - gemeni\n  - rednek\n  - rick ross\n  content: |\n    <p><a href="http://thefilth.us/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/Camo-Krooked-Make-The-Call.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-3815" title="Camo-Krooked-Make-The-Call" src="http://thefilth.us/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/Camo-Krooked-Make-The-Call-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></a></p>\n    <p>It&#8217;s been quite a week for new music and I cant wait to share what I&#8217;ve got for ya&#8217; this time. Along with Camo &amp; Krooked&#8217;s new EP I have some great Gemeni tracks and a lovely new Candy Land remix. Get your fill and be sure to leave me comments and responses.</p>\n    <p><a href="http://www.mediafire.com/file/k3vvv7ktz2155nd/01%20Hustlin%27%20%28Candy%20Land%20Remix%29.mp3">Rick Ross &#8211; Hustlin&#8217; (Candy Land Remix)</a></p>\n    <p>I want you to pay very close attention to these next three songs.</p>\n    <p><a href="http://www.mediafire.com/file/eaq7b1e8afb944d/Make%20The%20Call.mp3">Camo &amp; Krooked &#8211; Make The Call</a></p>\n    <p><a href="http://www.mediafire.com/file/g60215zma0dgft0/Make%20The%20Call%20%28Dubstep%20Mix%29.mp3">Camo &amp; Krooked &#8211; Make The Call (Dubstep Mix)</a></p>\n    <p><a href="http://www.mediafire.com/file/7t3h6dhsr1ipvwr/Make%20The%20Call%20%28Drum%20%26%20Bass%20Mix%29.mp3">Camo &amp; Krooked &#8211; Make The Call (Drum &amp; Bass Mix)</a></p>\n    <p>When producers can absolutely MURDER it in three very different genera, you know there headed to the top.</p>\n    <p><a href="http://www.mediafire.com/file/38asohynowr6nw8/Stop%20and%20Stare%20%28Gemini%20Remix%29.mp3">Fenech-Soler &#8211; Stop and Stare (Gemeni Remix)</a></p>\n    <p><a href="http://www.mediafire.com/file/1q50dz7t2yjh2am/You%20Need%20Me%2C%20I%20Dont%20Need%20You%20%28Gemini%20Remix%29.mp3">Ed Sheeran &#8211; You Need Me, I Don&#8217;t Need You (Gemeni Remix)</a></p>\n    <p><a href="http://www.mediafire.com/file/6fyo8dasojr3kuf/02%20Sound%20