\\" mesasge ;)</p>\\n\\\n    <p>As you may or may not remember,<strong> the full album download will only be available until Feb 21st</strong> - so DOWNLOAD IT WHILE YOU CAN. We'll be removing it from the server, and all of these tracks will be stream only etc etc - the idea here is that the artists regain ownership of the tracks, so hopefully they can find a home on some\\xC2\\xA0respectable\\xC2\\xA0label (and maybe we'll report on the track a 3rd time then heh)</p>\\n\\\n    <p>But to bring a different perspective on the release, we talked to a few of the artists that were involved with OAN - Vol 1. to bring a little backstory, enjoy the history &amp; some choice tracks.</p>\\n\\\n    <hr />\\n\\\n    <h3><strong>3 A.M.</strong></h3>\\n\\\n    <p>A project of 3 Torontians, <strong>3.A.M</strong> has been giving away free originals and remixes for the past few months. They've had some decent attention within the blogsphere and are hoping to build on it with this latest entitled \\"<em>Almost French</em>\\". Expect some official releases and more free tracks from these guys very soon.</p>\\n\\\n    <p><div class=\\"player-links\\">\\n  <div class=\\"track-single page-feed\\">\\n          <a href=\\"http://files2.earmilk.com/tracks/MjAxMi0wMS8wOSBBbG1vc3QgRnJlbmNoLm1wMw==.mp3\\" class=\\"player-link download\\" title=\\"Download\\">\\n        Download<span></span>\\n      </a>\\n                        <a href=\\"#play\\" class=\\"player-link play track\\" id=\\"link75657-0\\" title=\\"Play\\" onclick=\\"togglePlayById('75657-0');return false;\\">\\n      Play<span></span>\\n    </a>\\n    <span class=\\"player-link-title\\" id=\\"title75657-0\\" onclick=\\"togglePlayById('75657-0');return false;\\"><span class=\\"artist\\">3.A.M.</span> - Almost French  <span class='time'>(07:06)</span></span>\\n  </div>\\n  <div class=\\"clear\\"></div>\\n\\\n    </div><p><div class=\\"player-links\\">\\n  <div class=\\"track-single page-feed\\">\\n                  <a href=\\"http://soundcloud.com/3-a-m/metric-gold-guns-girls-3-a-m\\" target=\\"_blank\\" class=\\"player-link soundcloud\\" title=\\"Soundcloud\\">\\n        SC<span></span>\\n      </a>\\n                <a href=\\"http://api.soundcloud.com/tracks/24395287/download?consumer_key=05c76df9f7dc61bd4981517dc069adee\\" class=\\"player-link soundcloud-download\\" title=\\"Soundcloud Download\\">\\n      Download<span></span>\\n    </a>\\n        <a href=\\"#play\\" class=\\"player-link play track\\" id=\\"link75657-3\\" title=\\"Play\\" onclick=\\"togglePlayById('75657-3');return false;\\">\\n      Play<span></span>\\n    </a>\\n    <span class=\\"player-link-title\\" id=\\"title75657-3\\" onclick=\\"togglePlayById('75657-3');return false;\\"><span class=\\"artist\\">Metric</span> - Gold Guns Girls (3.A.M. Remix) <span class=\\"time\\">(05:07)</span></span>\\n  </div>\\n  <div class=\\"clear\\"></div>\\n\\\n    </div></p>\\n\\\n    <ul>\\n\\\n    <li><a href=\\"http://soundcloud.com/3-a-m\\">soundcloud.com/3-a-m</a></li>\\n\\\n    <li><a href=\\"http://www.facebook.com/theofficial3am\\">facebook.com/theofficial3am</a></li>\\n\\\n    </ul>\\n\\\n    <hr />\\n\\\n    <h3><strong>B\\xCE\\x94SSCULT</strong></h3>\\n\\\n    <p>From producers <strong>Kill Them With Colour</strong> comes\\xC2\\xA0<strong>B\\xCE\\x94SSCULT</strong>.\\xC2\\xA0Although a\\xC2\\xA0definite\\xC2\\xA0divergence from the norm for this Toronto operation, one can still hear\\xC2\\xA0familiar\\xC2\\xA0tones, sub-bases, and that proven quality that layers all these tracks. KTWC has lead itself down a musically-unworldly path sought out by very few in an effort to bring bass to the mortals (so they say), but give it a listen &amp; \\"<em>Grab a Hold\\"</em> of something.</p>\\n\\\n    <p><div class=\\"player-links\\">\\n  <div class=\\"track-single page-feed\\">\\n          <a href=\\"http://files2.earmilk.com/tracks/MjAxMi0wMS8xMiBHcmFiIEEgSG9sZC5tcDM=.mp3\\" class=\\"player-link download\\" title=\\"Download\\">\\n   