10	Winnie Cooper	Music, Interviews, Arts, Videos, Winnie tv, Party Photos, Mixes, Vancouver, No More Strangers, Events, Listings, Free Music Downloads!	--- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSS \nentries: \n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: Sam\n  categories: \n  - Music\n  - After You\n  - Meg Myers\n  - Valentines Day\n  content: "<p><img class=\\"alignnone\\" title=\\"Meg Myers \\" src=\\"http://winniecooper.net/sam/2011/12/img/MegMyers.jpg\\" alt=\\"Meg Myers \\" width=\\"491\\" height=\\"326\\" /></p>\\n\\\n    <p>Don\\xE2\\x80\\x99t even front.\\xC2\\xA0 We all know that at some point in time your romantic attraction to another individual forced you to become an amateur Internet stalker.\\xC2\\xA0 That\\xE2\\x80\\x99s why <a href=\\"http://meginthedark.tumblr.com/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Meg Myers </a>new song \\xE2\\x80\\x9CAfter You\\xE2\\x80\\x9D is so perfectly fitting for our everyday lives.</p>\\n\\\n    <p>There isn\\xE2\\x80\\x99t much to know about Myers besides the fact that she grew up in Tennessee as a practicing Jehovah Witness who never finished High School. \\xC2\\xA0Oh, and the babe can really sing.</p>\\n\\\n    <p>\\xE2\\x80\\x9CAfter You\\xE2\\x80\\x9D is like the ultimate strip tease. \\xC2\\xA0It starts off slow with a hypnotic piano ballad where Meg seductively whispers \\xE2\\x80\\x9CI\\xE2\\x80\\x99ll show you that my heart is real\\xE2\\x80\\x9D.\\xC2\\xA0 Then it gradually builds up the sexual tension, as she\\xE2\\x80\\x99ll do anything just to get lost with you.\\xC2\\xA0 And when the chorus drops a few seconds later, the panties do too. It\\xE2\\x80\\x99s delicately aggressive; as Meg warns her paying customers that her love is after them.</p>\\n\\\n    <p><img class=\\"alignnone\\" title=\\"Meg Myers \\" src=\\"http://winniecooper.net/sam/2011/12/img/megmyers6.jpg\\" alt=\\"Meg Myers \\" width=\\"491\\" height=\\"326\\" /></p>\\n\\\n    <p>So, if you\\xE2\\x80\\x99ve ever looked through his text messages, stolen a sweater to remember his scent, or just\\xC2\\xA0crept a particular Facebook profile a few too many times, this song is for you.</p>\\n\\\n    <p><a href=\\"http://winniecooper.net/sam/2011/12/music/AfterYou.mp3\\">\\xC2\\xA0Meg Myers &#8211; After You\\xC2\\xA0</a></p>\\n\\\n    <p>posted by <a href=\\"http://twitter.com/clarkbs\\">@clarkbs</a></p>\\n\\\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\\n\\n\\\n    \\t\\t\\t\\t<!-- Social Sharing Toolkit v2.0.4 | http://www.marijnrongen.com/wordpress-plugins/social_sharing_toolkit/ -->\\n\\\n    \\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"mr_social_sharing_wrapper\\"><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><iframe src=\\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?locale=en_US&amp;href=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fmeg-myers-after-you%2F&amp;layout=standard&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=51px&amp;height=24px\\" scrolling=\\"no\\" frameborder=\\"0\\" style=\\"border:none; overflow:hidden; width:51px; height:24px;\\" allowTransparency=\\"true\\"></iframe></span><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><div id=\\"fb-root\\"></div><fb:send href=\\"http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/meg-myers-after-you/\\" font=\\"\\"></fb:send></span><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><a href=\\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fmeg-myers-after-you%2F&amp;text=Meg+Myers+%E2%80%93+After+You&amp;via=winnie_cooper\\" target=\\"_blank\\" class=\\"mr_social_sharing_popup_link\\"><img src=\\"http://winniecooper.net/wp-content/plugins/social-sharing-toolkit/images/buttons/twitter.png\\" alt=\\"Share on Twitter\\" title=\\"Share on Twitter\\"/></a></span><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><g:plusone size=\\"medium\\" href=\\"http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/meg-myers-after-you/\\"></g:plusone></span><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><a href=\\"http://www.tumblr.com/share/link?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fmeg-myers-after-you%2F&amp;name=Meg+Myers+%E2%80%93+After+You\\" target=\\"_blank\\" class=\\"mr_social_sharing_popup_link\\"><i