 their BandCamp here. Horses (HUMANS Remix) by FluidArt Horses (Tribe of Zebras Remix) by FluidArt Empty Spaces (Oh No! Yoko Remix) by FluidArt Posted by John\n  title: Yes Nice Remixed\n  url: http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/yes-nice-remixed/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: Wobangs\n  categories: \n  - Events\n  - Music\n  - Anti-Valentines Day\n  - Beatroute\n  - Gold & Youth\n  - Philoceraptor\n  - The Biltmore\n  - Watermelon\n  content: |-\n    <p><img src="https://fbcdn-sphotos-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-snc7/s320x320/425488_359214604090871_210374692308197_1429071_2031441081_n.jpg" alt="" width="381" height="588" /></p>\n    <p>Hate Valentines Day? Most of us do. Well we&#8217;ve got the perfect solution for you! Our good friends over at <a title="BEATROUTE" href="http://beatroute.ca" target="_blank">BeatRoute</a> are throwing an Anti-Valentines day party this Monday at The Biltmore appropriately titled &#8220;<a title="Anti-Valentines Day " href="https://www.facebook.com/events/243399219067452/" target="_blank">The Nightmare before Valentines Day</a>&#8220;. Featuring <a title="GOLD AND YOUTH" href="http://goldandyouth.com/" target="_blank">GOLD &amp; YOUTH&#8217;</a>s first show (formerly The Raccoons), they just signed to Arts &amp; Crafts and local faves <a title="Philoceraptor" href="http://philoceraptor.com/" target="_blank">PHILOCERRAPTOR </a>&amp; <a title="Watermelon" href="http://watermelon.bandcamp.com/" target="_blank">WATERMELON</a> + djs. All for only 8$, so let&#8217;s all celebrate being lonely together!</p>\n    <p><iframe width="500" height="281" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/_SgGrM51kLk?fs=1&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\n    <p><strong>Posted by </strong><a title="wobeezy" href="https://twitter.com/#!/Tehrealwobangs" target="_blank">Matea</a></p>\n    \n    \t\t\t\t<!-- Social Sharing Toolkit v2.0.4 | http://www.marijnrongen.com/wordpress-plugins/social_sharing_toolkit/ -->\n    \t\t\t\t<div class="mr_social_sharing_wrapper"><span class="mr_social_sharing"><iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?locale=en_US&amp;href=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fanti-valentines-day-show-3%2F&amp;layout=standard&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=51px&amp;height=24px" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:51px; height:24px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe></span><span class="mr_social_sharing"><div id="fb-root"></div><fb:send href="http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/anti-valentines-day-show-3/" font=""></fb:send></span><span class="mr_social_sharing"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fanti-valentines-day-show-3%2F&amp;text=ANTI-VALENTINES+DAY+SHOW+%3C%2F3&amp;via=winnie_cooper" target="_blank" class="mr_social_sharing_popup_link"><img src="http://winniecooper.net/wp-content/plugins/social-sharing-toolkit/images/buttons/twitter.png" alt="Share on Twitter" title="Share on Twitter"/></a></span><span class="mr_social_sharing"><g:plusone size="medium" href="http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/anti-valentines-day-show-3/"></g:plusone></span><span class="mr_social_sharing"><a href="http://www.tumblr.com/share/link?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fanti-valentines-day-show-3%2F&amp;name=ANTI-VALENTINES+DAY+SHOW+%3C%2F3" target="_blank" class="mr_social_sharing_popup_link"><img src="http://winniecooper.net/wp-content/plugins/social-sharing-toolkit/images/buttons/tumblr.png" alt="Share on Tumblr" title="Share on Tumblr"/></a></span></div>\n  entry_id: http://winniecooper.net/?p=16636\n  published: 2012-02-12 23:33:25 Z\n  summary: Hate Valentines Day? Most of us do. Well we&#8217;ve got the perfect solution for you! Our good friends over at BeatRoute are throwing an Anti-Valentines day party this Monday at The Biltmore appropriately titled &#8220;The Nightmare before Valentines Day&#8220;. Featuring GOLD &#38; YOUTH&#8217;s first show (formerly The Raccoons), they just signed to Arts &#38; Crafts [...]\n  title: ANTI-VALENTINES DAY SHOW </3\n  url: http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/anti-valentines-day-show-3/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: Sam\n  categories: \n  - Music\n  - Big Mouth\n  - diplo\n  - Master of My Make-Believe\n  - Santigold\n  - switch\n  content: "<p><img class=\\"alignnone\\" title=\\"Sanigold\\" src=\\"http://winniecooper.net/sam/2011/12/img/Santigold2.jpg\\" alt=\\"Santigold\\" width=\\"467\\" height=\\"280\\" /></p>\\n\\\n    <p>A few years ago I wrote a paper in which I discussed and subsequently dissected the current state of women in hip-hop.\\xC2\\xA0 I eventually came to the conclusion that my fellow gender counteparts were about to take back what was rightfully theirs. \\xC2\\xA0The reasoning behind this you ask?\\xC2\\xA0 Well that\\xE2\\x80\\x99s easy, her name is Santigold.</p>\\n\\\n    <p>Santigold (formerly Santogold) released her debut album in 2008 and that shit was all kinds of cray.\\xC2\\xA0 It blended everything from reggae to indie pop and featured some of the industries biggest names, including Diplo and Switch.\\xC2\\xA0 She co-wrote and produced the entire album and once again made female empowerment an endearing quality.</p>\\n\\\n    <p><img class=\\"alignnone\\" title=\\"Santigold - Big Mouth\\" src=\\"http://winniecooper.net/sam/2011/12/img/Bigmouth1.jpg\\" alt=\\"Santigold - Big Mouth\\" width=\\"487\\" height=\\"293\\" /></p>\\n\\\n    <p>As of late, Santigold has been working on her follow up album \\xE2\\x80\\x9CMaster of My Make-Believe\\xE2\\x80\\x9D, which is expected for a spring release.\\xC2\\xA0 The first single \\xE2\\x80\\x9CBig Mouth\\xE2\\x80\\x9D dropped last month and with it she reclaims the meaning behind bad ass bitch.\\xC2\\xA0 It\\xE2\\x80\\x99s reminiscent of old-school Missy Elliot and the subtle stabs at her misguided haters is pure genius.\\xC2\\xA0 This is one fantasy I definitely want to be apart of.</p>\\n\\\n    <p><iframe src=\\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/cxdQ_uD5IWk\\" frameborder=\\"0\\" width=\\"450\\" height=\\"259\\"></iframe></p>\\n\\\n    <p><a href=\\"http://winniecooper.net/sam/2011/12/music/SantigoldBigMouth.mp3\\">Santigold &#8211; Big Mouth\\xC2\\xA0</a></p>\\n\\\n    <p>Download the track for free\\xC2\\xA0<a href=\\"http://www.santigold.com/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">here</a>.</p>\\n\\\n    <p>posted by <a href=\\"http://twitter.com/clarkbs\\">@clarkbs</a></p>\\n\\n\\\n    \\t\\t\\t\\t<!-- Social Sharing Toolkit v2.0.4 | http://www.marijnrongen.com/wordpress-plugins/social_sharing_toolkit/ -->\\n\\\n    \\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"mr_social_sharing_wrapper\\"><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><iframe src=\\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?locale=en_US&amp;href=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fsantigold-big-mouth%2F&amp;layout=standard&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=51px&amp;height=24px\\" scrolling=\\"no\\" frameborder=\\"0\\" style=\\"border:none; overflow:hidden; width:51px; height:24px;\\" allowTransparency=\\"true\\"></iframe></span><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><div id=\\"fb-root\\"></div><fb:send href=\\"http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/santigold-big-mouth/\\" font=\\"\\"></fb:send></span><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><a href=\\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fsantigold-big-mouth%2F&amp;text=Santigold+%E2%80%93+Big+Mouth&amp;via=winnie_cooper\\" target=\\"_blank\\" class=\\"mr_social_sharing_popup_link\\"><img src=\\"http://winniecooper.net/wp-content/plugins/social-sharing-toolkit/images/buttons/twitter.png\\" alt=\\"Share on Twitter\\" title=\\"Share on Twitter\\"/></a></span><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><g:plusone size=\\"medium\\" href=\\"http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/santigold-big-mouth/\\"></g:plusone></span><span class=\\"mr_social_sharing\\"><a href=\\"http://www.tumblr.com/share/link?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fsantigold-big-mouth%2F&amp;name=Santigold+%E2%80%93+Big+Mouth\\" target=\\"_blank\\" class=\\"mr_social_sharing_popup_link\\"><img src=\\"http://winniecooper.net/wp-content/plugins/social-sharing-toolkit/images/buttons/tumblr.png\\" alt=\\"Share on Tumblr\\" title=\\"Share on Tumblr\\"/></a></span></div>"\n  entry_id: http://winniecooper.net/?p=16542\n  published: 2012-02-10 20:00:21 Z\n  summary: "A few years ago I wrote a paper in which I discussed and subsequently dissected the current state of women in hip-hop.\\xC2\\xA0 I eventually came to the conclusion that my fellow gender counteparts were about to take back what was rightfully theirs. \\xC2\\xA0The reasoning behind this you ask?\\xC2\\xA0 Well that\\xE2\\x80\\x99s easy, her name is Santigold. [...]"\n  title: "Santigold \\xE2\\x80\\x93 Big Mouth"\n  url: http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/santigold-big-mouth/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: John\n  categories: \n  - Events\n  - Music\n  - behind sapphire\n  - events\n  - John\n  - Music Series\n  - Original Spin\n  - rococode\n  - the gay nineties\n  - Ville Kulla\n  - yvr\n  content: |-\n    <p><img class="aligncenter" src="http://winniecooper.net/john/Images/14/OS Music Series.jpg" alt="" width="258" height="368" /></p>\n    <p>Winnie Cooper is sponsoring a local music series hosted by our friends at <a title="Official" href="http://www.originalspin.ca/" target="_blank">Original Spin</a>. From February 10 &#8211; 18th at <a title="Official" href="http://www.cafedeuxsoleils.com/" target="_blank">Cafe Deux Soleils</a> you&#8217;ll be able to hear some of Vancouver&#8217;s best bands including <a title="BandCamp" href="http://villekulla.bandcamp.com/" target="_blank">Ville Kulla</a>, <a title="Official" href="http://rococode.com/" target="_blank">Rococode</a>, and <a title="BandCamp" href="http://thegaynineties.bandcamp.com/" target="_blank">The Gay Nineties</a>.</p>\n    <p><a title="Ville Kulla - Braves" href="http://winniecooper.net/john/Mp3/14/Original Spin - volume 1 - 03 Braves.mp3" target="_blank">Ville Kulla &#8211; Braves</a><br />\n    <a title="Rococode - Empire" href="http://winniecooper.net/john/Mp3/14/Original Spin - volume 1 - 06 Empire.mp3" target="_blank">Rococode &#8211; Empire</a><br />\n    <a title="The Gay Nineties - Favourite Game" href="http://winniecooper.net/john/Mp3/14/Original Spin - volume 1 - 02 Favorite Game.mp3" target="_blank">The Gay Nineties &#8211; Favourite Game</a></p>\n    <p>Three bands/night for eight days? Sounds good to me. Individual tix are $10 a pop and an eight days pass is a measly $25; steal. The bands are also giving away a free compilation album on Original Spins&#8217; BandCamp page <a title="BandCamp" href="http://originalspin.bandcamp.com/" target="_blank">right hurr</a>. Also, see the Facebook event page for a full list of bands <a title="Facebook Event Page" href="https://www.facebook.com/events/303782812967296/" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>\n    <p><img class="alignnone" src="http://fc00.deviantart.net/fs70/f/2010/271/a/1/adventure_time_gif_6_by_a_new_hope-d2zpfkq.gif" alt="" width="500" height="311" /></p>\n    <p>Posted by <em>John</em></p>\n    \n    \t\t\t\t<!-- Social Sharing Toolkit v2.0.4 | http://www.marijnrongen.com/wordpress-plugins/social_sharing_toolkit/ -->\n    \t\t\t\t<div class="mr_social_sharing_wrapper"><span class="mr_social_sharing"><iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?locale=en_US&amp;href=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Foriginal-spins-music-series%2F&amp;layout=standard&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=51px&amp;height=24px" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:51px; height:24px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe></span><span class="mr_social_sharing"><div id="fb-root"></div><fb:send href="http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/original-spins-music-series/" font=""></fb:send></span><span class="mr_social_sharing"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecoope