iginal song, and i am really happy with how my remix came out as well. i hope you enjoy it! DOWNLOAD MY &#8220;OPEN THE DOOR&#8221; REMIX NOW! AND OPEN THE DOOR!&#8221;</em></p>\n    <p>I like how he referred to Black Marble as a &#8220;cold synth&#8221; act instead of goth. There&#8217;s hope out there for you lil gothies after all. Time to see all your goth stocks and invest in cold syths!</p>\n    <p>via <a href="http://plainpictures.blogspot.com">Pictureplane&#8217;s blog</a>.<br />\n    <iframe src="http://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F35770064&amp;show_artwork=true" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="166"></iframe></p>\n    <p><a href="http://winniecooper.net/hunk/feb/Pretender.mp3">Black Marble &#8211; Pretender</a></p>\n    <p><iframe src="http://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F32954989&amp;auto_play=false&amp;show_artwork=true&amp;color=e9637c" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="166"></iframe></p>\n    <p>posted by <a href="http://twitter.com/tristanorchard">@tristanorchard</a></p>\n    \n    \t\t\t\t<!-- Social Sharing Toolkit v2.0.4 | http://www.marijnrongen.com/wordpress-plugins/social_sharing_toolkit/ -->\n    \t\t\t\t<div class="mr_social_sharing_wrapper"><span class="mr_social_sharing"><iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?locale=en_US&amp;href=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fnew-from-pictureplane%2F&amp;layout=standard&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=51px&amp;height=24px" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:51px; height:24px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe></span><span class="mr_social_sharing"><div id="fb-root"></div><fb:send href="http://winniecooper.net/2012/02/new-from-pictureplane/" font=""></fb:send></span><span class="mr_social_sharing"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniecooper.net%2F2012%2F02%2Fnew-from-pictureplane%2F&amp;text=New+From+P