e Mafia took over Pete Tong&#8217;s essential mix on this wonderful friday night. Not only did they kill it, but they also brought a mouse along. Deadmau5 came through with a sick set to make this full mix a MUST DOWNLOAD. We already heard Swedish House Mafia&#8217;s new single &#8220;Greyhound&#8221; which was premiered on [...]\n  title: Swedish House Mafia Essential Mix ft. Deadmau5 Set *MUST DOWNLOAD*\n  url: http://yesgoodmusic.com/2012/02/18/swedish-house-mafia-essential-mix-ft-deadmau5-set-must-download/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: Raffi\n  categories: \n  - -Home-\n  - Genres\n  - Hip-Hop\n  - Rap\n  content: "<p><a href=\\"http://yesgoodmusic.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/kanye-west-tony-williams.jpg\\"><img class=\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9905\\" title=\\"kanye-west-tony-williams\\" src=\\"http://yesgoodmusic.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/kanye-west-tony-williams.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"540\\" height=\\"359\\" /></a></p>\\n\\\n    <p>Ok, since I&#8217;ve posted a good amount of EDM tracks today I thought I&#8217;d dig up some of my favorite hip-hop songs from <em>the last week or two</em> that I never got up on ygm. \\xC2\\xA0I&#8217;ll start off with a new Kanye feature on his cousin, Tony Williams album,\\xC2\\xA0<em>K<a href=\\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/id502728220?i=502728222&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\\" target=\\"_blank\\">ing Or The Fool</a>. \\xC2\\xA0</em>We heard a snippet of this track not too long ago, but the full version of &#8220;Another You&#8221; was released on iTunes (spotted on 2dopeboyz). \\xC2\\xA0Stream the track below and hit the jump to check out more of your daily dose of hip hop.<br />\\n\\\n    <script type=\\"text/javascript\\">// <![CDATA[\\n      var zippywww=\\"3\\";var zippyfile=\\"60247496\\";var zippytext=\\"#fc0000\\";var zippyback=\\"#edf0f0\\";var zippyplay=\\"#0f0fd9\\";var zippywidth=850;var zippyauto=false;var zippyvol=80;var zippywave = \\"#000000\\";var zippyborder = \\"#f7f