n  categories: \n  - Singles\n  - death and vanilla\n  content: "<p><a href=\\"http://pastaprima.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/DeathAndVanilla-Cover.jpg\\"><img class=\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-12761\\" title=\\"DeathAndVanilla-Cover\\" src=\\"http://pastaprima.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/DeathAndVanilla-Cover-500x500.jpg\\" alt=\\"DeathAndVanilla-Cover\\" width=\\"500\\" height=\\"500\\" /></a></p>\\n\\\n    <p>Sweden&#8217;s\\xC2\\xA0<strong><a title=\\"Quick Hits: Death And Vanilla\\" href=\\"http://pastaprima.net/artist-reviews/quick-hits-death-and-vanilla/\\">Death And Vanilla</a></strong>\\xC2\\xA0got me hooked a little ways back with their debut EP (<a href=\\"http://deathandvanilla.bandcamp.com/\\" onclick=\\"pageTracker._trackPageview('/outgoing/deathandvanilla.bandcamp.com/?referer=');\\">stream it</a>) which was filled with odd noir pop songs. \\xC2\\xA0They are now set to release their debut full length <em>S/T</em> LP via <strong><a href=\\"http://handsinthedarkrecords.com/\\" onclick=\\"pageTracker._trackPageview('/outgoing/handsinthedarkrecords.com/?referer=');\\">Hands In The Dark</a></strong> and <strong><a href=\\"http://www.kalligrammofon.com/\\" onclick=\\"pageTracker._trackPageview('/outgoing/www.kalligrammofon.com/?referer=');\\">Kalligrammofon</a></strong> (on March 13th &#8211; <a href=\\"http://handsinthedarkrecords.com/hitd/Store.html\\" onclick=\\"pageTracker._trackPageview('/outgoing/handsinthedarkrecords.com/hitd/Store.html?referer=');\\">pre-order</a>). \\xC2\\xA0They give us a first taste with the song &#8220;Rituals&#8221; &#8211; a decidedly murkier blend of what they were dishing out before. \\xC2\\xA0There&#8217;s a dark almost industrial coating worked into their already eerie sound that works so well. \\xC2\\xA0Take a listen/look:</p>\\n\\\n    <p><iframe src=\\"http://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F35620896&amp;show_artwork=true\\" frameborder=\\"no\\" scrolling=\\"no\\" width=