of the true meaning of Christmas. \\xC2\\xA0Better known for their work at the centre of modern [...]<img alt=\\"\\" border=\\"0\\" src=\\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=eatenbymonsters.wordpress.com&amp;blog=5170812&amp;post=1078&amp;subd=eatenbymonsters&amp;ref=&amp;feed=1\\" width=\\"1\\" height=\\"1\\" />"\n  title: "An Alt. Christmas 22: Spiers & Boden"\n  url: http://eatenbymonsters.wordpress.com/2011/12/22/an-alt-christmas-00-spiers-boden/\n- !ruby/object:Feedzirra::Parser::RSSEntry \n  author: Tom\n  categories: \n  - Alternative Christmas\n  - music\n  - christmas\n  - Withered Hand\n  content: "<p><em>[There's plenty of great Christmas songs out there, but most suffer terribly from over-exposure. \\xC2\\xA0To remedy that, EbM presents a selection of\\xC2\\xA0<a href=\\"http://eatenbymonsters.wordpress.com/category/alternative-christmas/\\">alternative Christmas songs</a>.]</em></p>\\n\\\n    <p><a href=\\"http://eatenbymonsters.files.wordpress.com/2011/12/withered-hand-11.jpg\\"><img class=\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1074\\" title=\\"SONY DSC\\" src=\\"http://eatenbymonsters.files.wordpress.com/2011/12/withered-hand-11.jpg?w=510&#038;h=341\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"510\\" height=\\"341\\" /></a></p>\\n\\\n    <p>Now we&#8217;re within sight of the finish line, it&#8217;s time to bring out the big guns; none of the songs in this festive selection have been anything less than good, but now is the time to take it up a notch. \\xC2\\xA0These last four tracks are not only great Christmas songs, but simply great songs, period. \\xC2\\xA0<a href=\\"http://witheredhand.com/\\">Withered Hand</a> (a.k.a. Dan Willson) have (has) just released a new Christmas song <a href=\\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FarG6Y0pkFk\\">on YouTube</a> called <em>Real Snow</em>, but it&#8217;s their (his) home-recorded effort from a couple of years ago that really struck a chord with me.</p>\\n\\\n    <p>Withered Hand &#8211; <a href=\\"http://www.bearfacedrecords.com/EbMBlog_m