45	Cypress Hill & Rusko - "Roll It, Light It" [Video]	\N	http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/earmilk/~3/RAL_KU8DI7Q/	<img src='http://earmilk.com/c/images/medium/you-just-dont-care.png' alt=''/><p></p>\n<p>Remember those days when you were young listening to <strong>Cypress Hill</strong>? Those times when "Rap/Rock Superstar" was playing at a house party, and every mindless idiot you knew could sing along to it? Right - so let's establish something: Cypress Hill is back with a style you've never heard from them. Teaming up with <strong>Rusko</strong> was a great idea. An even better idea? Not making it too dubsteppy.</p>\n<p>The execution of this song is only made better by Rusko's production - and I'm really not even a Rusko fan. This whole song actually make me respect Rusko a lot more than I used to. It's a glitchy, driving beat that borders more closely along the lines of a drum and bass feel, with dubstep timing. Then there's the undeniable old school influence of <strong>DJ Muggs</strong>, with <strong>Sen Dogg</strong> and <strong>B-Real</strong> chopping up vocals about the best way to smoke marijuana. (<em>Years later, Cypress Hill is still around to teach a new generation about smoking weed. Thank goodness</em>.)</p>\n<p>The video itself is supremely directed and edited. The glitchy train shots of Southern California, along with the spooky shots inside an old building, really bring out the dark and pounding nature of this song. The whole process was directed by French native <strong><a href="http://www.jodeb.ca/" target="_blank">Jonathan Desbiens</a> </strong>(his demo reel might just be the best I have ever seen). It's a bit of a departure from his usual work with Le Cirque De Soleil, but equally visually stunning. Desbiens is, in my opinion, probably the biggest rising star of this whole video. Cypress Hill and Rusko are "made", but the talent of Jodeb is really what makes this whole thing pop as a product. Roll it, light it? I think I will.</p>\n<p><div class="embed-video embed-youtube"><iframe width="592" height="340" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/iX9MG86lg44?&rel=0&version=3&enablejsapi=1&theme=dark&modestbranding=1&hd=1&autohide=1&color=white&showinfo=0"frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/earmilk/~4/RAL_KU8DI7Q" height="1" width="1"/>	3	\N	\N	2012-02-22 17:01:30	2012-02-23 05:29:17.814062	cypress-hill-and-rusko-roll-it-light-it-video	you-just-dont-care.png	2012-02-23 05:29:17.707140
